snippet.title: [PS2 Longplay] .hack//INFECTION Part 1
snippet.description:
This is the special project that I talked about earlier. I decided that I wanted to take on the .Hack series. Once I've finished this, game I'll move on to the other three.

Here in part 1, I go over the tutorials and I also clear a dungeon with BlackRose. I tried to attempt a random field that was just a level above me. It went well for a little bit, until I ended up with too many enemies and me and BlackRose died. The video seems to lag somewhat, but it doesn't seem to lag all that much. Until then, subscribe and Enjoy!!
